<div class="col five-sm clear">
<h2 id="section-top">Overview</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContentb654fe888afc40ad96a0004ace05fe97">
<div class="profile-pic">
<img alt="St Michael's Hospital" border="0" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_column1Content_column1Content_SummaryAndPhotoModule_PhotoView_DisplayImage" src="/Services/UserControls/UploadHandlers/MediaServerHandler.ashx?id=9738"/>
</div>
</div>
<p>St Michael's Hospital offers a centre of excellence in Cornwall for the breast care and planned orthopaedic surgery.</p>
<p>The Hospital also provides a wide range of outpatient services including 'one-stop' pre-assessment clinics allowing suitable patients to be fast-tracked for orthopaedic operations.</p></div>
</div>
</div>
